## Layout & Spacing

**Containers**: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8` (main), `max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4` (forms)

**Spacing Scale**: gap-2 (8px), gap-3 (12px), gap-4 (16px), gap-6 (24px), p-2/4/6 (8/16/24px), mb-2/4/6/8 (8/16/24/32px)

**Grid/Flex**: Two column `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6`, Three column `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`, Responsive stack `flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4`

## Shadows & Elevation

Use Forvis-branded shadows: `shadow-corporate` (subtle), `shadow-corporate-md` (medium), `shadow-corporate-lg` (high)

## Borders & Rounded

**Radius**: `rounded-lg` (8px) for most, `rounded-full` for badges

**Colors**: `border-forvis-gray-200` (default), `border-forvis-gray-300` (inputs), `border-forvis-blue-500` (focus)

