## Accessibility

**Focus**: Always `focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-forvis-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2`
**Contrast**: WCAG AA - text on white use gray-700+, text on blue-500 use white
**Screen Reader**: `className="sr-only"` for hidden content, ARIA labels for icons

## Responsive

**Breakpoints**: sm (640px), md (768px), lg (1024px), xl (1280px), 2xl (1536px)

**Mobile-First**: `flex flex-col md:flex-row`, `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2`, `hidden md:block`

